race.comment: SETTLE FOR LESS (8) is in hot form after clocking a dominant 27.07 victory two back then followed up with a 26.84 win at Horsham over 485m last time. Flying lately and expected to go close again. WITCH OF NOVA (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (23.04) last time in a Grade 5 at Warragul. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. ASTON ALLURE (7) was a Grade 5 winner two back then out of the placings latest at this track but moves to Box 7 this time where she has performed well. Can feature with the right run. HE'S ALL THAT (1) must be included in main hopes on latest effort.
